Today, I got a hold of the best photo possible.

33
00:02:18,870 --> 00:02:23,000
Please excuse us for blurring out the photo since it's too shocking.

34
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:25,010
Let's take a look first.

35
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:32,870
