76
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:02,120
That's right.

77
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:06,050
I have received a tip from a reliable source that Ms. Baek is the daughter of Gong In Woo.

78
00:05:06,050 --> 00:05:09,450
Are you saying Ms. J is Gong In Woo's secret mistress?

79
00:05:09,450 --> 00:05:10,420
That's right.

80
