You saw the broadcast, didn't you? Everyone was excitedly talking about it.

92
00:06:48,020 --> 00:06:52,950
Thanks to me, the media outlets must have made a lot of money.

93
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:58,500
Are you okay?

94
00:06:58,500 --> 00:07:04,190
Why? Oh, right. Because that photo was revealed?

95
00:07:04,190 --> 00:07:10,280
Tell them to do whatever they want. What can they do with just one photo?

96
00:07:11,110 --> 00:07:14,820
Don't worry and just take good care of the rest of the photos.

97
00:07:14,820 --> 00:07:17,630
Don't create unnecessary issues.

98
00:07:17,630 --> 00:07:19,750
Aren't you worried about Sang Ah?

99
00:07:19,750 --> 00:07:22,380
What about her?

100
00:07:23,520 --> 00:07:31,220
Your daughter is being pegged as a copycat criminal who followed in the steps of her father's murders.

101
00:07:31,220 --> 00:07:34,590
It's the worst situation with the second hearing coming up.

102
00:07:34,590 --> 00:07:40,860
That's your expertise. Like you protected me, protect her, too.

103
00:07:40,860 --> 00:07:44,590
That's why you became a lawyer, isn't it?

104
00:07:49,020 --> 00:07:53,110
Even if it doesn't go well, don't be distraught.

105
00:07:53,110 --> 00:07:56,470
Sang Ah is my work of art.

106
00:07:56,470 --> 00:07:59,390
She's a masterpiece.

107
00:08:00,350 --> 00:08:07,450
Like my paintings, even after time passes, she'll remain as a work of art.

108
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:13,910
Gong In Woo...

109
00:08:15,030 --> 00:08:19,330
I thought you were some kind of a god.

110
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:27,350
When you killed my sexually abusive stepfather for me saying that you'd  save me by shedding blood,

111
00:08:27,350 --> 00:08:33,860
I really felt saved. I felt like I was reborn.

112
00:08:33,860 --> 00:08:40,330
That's right. I think I saw a halo of some kind over you back then.

113
00:08:40,330 --> 00:08:41,870
What are you talking about right—

114
00:08:41,870 --> 00:08:46,610
Whenever I was able to obtain more things and climb higher,

115
00:08:46,610 --> 00:08:51,200
I thought you had made it happen for me.

116
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:55,550
So that's why I kept looking up to you and doing whatever you asked of me.

117
00:09:06,100 --> 00:09:14,600
You're just... a perverted idiot who's crazy about murder.

118
00:09:15,500 --> 00:09:22,860
What? You dare treat your daughter the same way as your lousy paintings?

119
00:09:22,860 --> 00:09:27,440
You don't care about your daughter, whether she shares your blood or not.

120
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:32,770
You crazy bastard, just spend the rest of your life in there.

121
00:09:32,770 --> 00:09:37,390
Until you rot and decay, die in there!

122
00:09:43,030 --> 00:09:47,210
No... don't you dare come out even after you die.

123
00:09:54,170 --> 00:09:56,620
Jang Hye Mi...

124
00:09:56,620 --> 00:09:59,240
Hye Mi!

125
00:10:49,880 --> 00:10:51,640
Again?

126
00:10:51,640 --> 00:10:54,460
By releasing it to the media, we only got tons more useless leads.

127
00:10:54,460 --> 00:10:59,930
Not like we can ignore them. It's such a waste of time! Why didn't you stop them?

128
00:10:59,930 --> 00:11:03,460
I didn't know this was what the butterfly effect meant.

129
00:11:03,460 --> 00:11:08,420
Instead of a typhoon, the mail keeps pouring in.

130
00:11:10,320 --> 00:11:12,700
And also, why are there

131
