There was no return address, so it'll be difficult to find out.

137
00:11:52,520 --> 00:11:53,490
We have all 10 cases?

138
00:11:53,490 --> 00:11:55,850
Yes, all 10.

139
00:11:55,850 --> 00:11:57,560
Okay then.

140
00:11:57,560 --> 00:12:01,090
Even if we can't put him behind bars, we should be able to get him good!

