April 2008...

145
00:12:19,130 --> 00:12:22,180
Huh? Then that's within the statute of limitations.

146
00:12:22,180 --> 00:12:24,770
What? Then we can put Gong In Woo behind bars?

147
00:12:24,770 --> 00:12:29,150
Prepare to indict him for an 11th case.

148
00:12:29,150 --> 00:12:31,830
Yes!

149
00:12:34,150 --> 00:12:35,510
Please give us a statement!

150
00:12:39,460 --> 00:12:41,690
Just one photo has caused an uproar,

151
00:12:41,690 --> 00:12:46,940
and the murders of Gong In Woo from 32 years ago have all been confirmed.

152
00:12:46,940 --> 00:12:52,270
Not only that, but new evidence has also come to light for another case within the statute of limitations

153
00:12:52,270 --> 00:12:56,540
and Gong In Woo will now stand trial as a defendant again.

154
00:13:04,150 --> 00:13:08,720
Today must be a special day. You look so happy.

155
00:13:08,720 --> 00:13:11,700
Yes, I'm going to confess to someone I like.

156
00:13:11,700 --> 00:13:13,280
Oh, I hope all goes well.

157
00:13:13,280 --> 00:13:15,610
Here. I wish you the best.

158
00:13:15,610 --> 00:13:18,490
Thank you.

159
00:13:33,350 --> 00:13:34,820
 No, stay away! 

160
00:13:34,820 --> 00:13:37,150
 Hyeong Bin, it's Gong Ji Cheol. 

161
00:14:15,180 --> 00:14:18,360
Sa Bin?

162
00:14:18,360 --> 00:14:20,400
Oh, she's here.

163
00:14:20,400 --> 00:14:23,830
She usually doesn't pick up when she's drinking.

164
00:14:23,830 --> 00:14:27,200
Okay then. Come here.

165
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:31,900
♫   My dear, you're going to leave me   ♫

