00:15:29,080 --> 00:15:32,920
There's such a thing as loyalty!

182
00:15:32,920 --> 00:15:34,620
So? Keep going.

183
00:15:34,620 --> 00:15:38,150
She just feels sorry for him whenever she sees him.

184
00:15:38,150 --> 00:15:41,920
She feels bad and worries about him, and wants to hug him.

185
00:15:41,920 --> 00:15:47,840
So... whenever she sees him, her heart hurts.

186
00:15:47,840 --> 00:15:52,030
So, her heart beats for one man,

187
00:15:52,030 --> 00:15:54,930
and for the other, her heart hurts?

188
00:15:54,930 --> 00:15:56,690
That's it.

189
00:15:56,690 --> 00:15:59,460
Now, tell me.

190
00:15:59,460 --> 00:16:05,880
Uncles, which one do you think is real love?

191
00:16:06,680 --> 00:16:08,110
- Beating! 
 - Hurting!

192
00:16:08,110 --> 00:16:11,230
Do you want her to have a painful love

193
00:16:11,230 --> 00:16:16,540
or beautiful love? At her age, a beating heart is real love.

194
00:16:16,540 --> 00:16:19,500
Hey, that's why you don't know love.

195
00:16:19,500 --> 00:16:23,090
Excitement is short-lived and sadness is long-lasting.

196
00:16:23,090 --> 00:16:26,760
If you're to live together for life, you have to go for the long-lasting.

197
00:16:26,760 --> 00:16:29,710
Sa Bin, what do you think?

198
00:16:29,710 --> 00:16:31,830
She's sleeping.

199
00:16:35,410 --> 00:16:37,260
Our Jong Beom!

200
00:16:37,260 --> 00:16:40,080
Your timing is not so great!

201
00:16:40,080 --> 00:16:43,330
You're here?

202
00:16:43,330 --> 00:16:44,890
What happened to...

203
00:16:44,890 --> 00:16:47,460
Sa Bin is...

