00:17:01,510 --> 00:17:05,610
Gong Ji Cheol's name was cleared today.

205
00:17:05,610 --> 00:17:08,030
Thirty-two years later.

206
00:17:09,310 --> 00:17:15,990
When this day came, I thought I could come to you without any shame.

207
00:17:17,120 --> 00:17:19,410
But it wasn't true.

208
00:17:21,700 --> 00:17:27,650
To you, I'm still a murderer.

209
00:17:30,960 --> 00:17:36,830
