210
00:17:38,040 --> 00:17:40,950
In front of you at that.

211
00:17:44,400 --> 00:17:51,850
Someone who remembers the worst part of me, why did it have to be you?

212
00:17:55,470 --> 00:18:02,710
When I think about that, I don't feel like I can ever come to you.

213
00:18:26,640 --> 00:18:28,660
Oh, my head!

214
00:18:29,840 --> 00:18:31,610
Did I teleport?

215
00:18:31,610 --> 00:18:35,600
I know I was drinking at Uncles' place.

216
00:18:40,350 --> 00:18:41,640
You're crazy, aren't you?

217
00:18:41,640 --> 00:18:44,730
My head is going to split! Why are you hitting my head?

218
00:18:44,730 --> 00:18:47,250
Then I should just hit you on your back! You're nuts!

219
00:18:47,250 --> 00:18:48,570
You're insane!

220
00:18:48,570 --> 00:18:50,830
Now you drink and get piggybacked here by your student?

221
00:18:50,830 --> 00:18:53,010
Student? Who?

222
00:18:53,010 --> 00:18:54,420
Jong Beom?

223
00:18:54,420 --> 00:18:56,050
He carried me here?

224
00:18:56,050 --> 00:18:58,620
That's right. Your stalker student.

225
00:18:58,620 --> 00:19:01,670
Because of you, my blood will dry up and I'll become remains myself!

226
00:19:01,670 --> 00:19:05,860
Then that wasn't a dream?

227
00:19:05,860 --> 00:19:10,080
What's with your response? You're making me nervous.

228
00:19:10,080 --> 00:19:16,330
I... heard something strange from Jong Beom.

229
00:19:20,710 --> 00:19:26,060
 In order to save you, I killed Yoon Jeong Hee. 

230
00:19:28,580 --> 00:19:34,210
  I wanted to give her heart to you. 

231
00:19:36,980 --> 00:19:43,490
 Yoon Jeong Hee was a bad mother who killed her own child. 

232
00:19:49,710 --> 00:19:55,880
 Even when I went to the snowy hill to seek salvation from you, 

233
00:19:55,880 --> 00:20:00,720
 everyone said I went to kill you. 

234
00:20:00,720 --> 00:20:07,330
 I only wanted to confess to you for the last time and give you my heart. 

235
00:20:07,330 --> 00:20:11,260
 I... I am... 

236
00:20:16,590 --> 00:20:18,620
 Gong Ji Cheol! 

237
00:20:27,940 --> 00:20:30,220
 No! 

238
00:20:31,340 --> 00:20:34,480
 No one gave me a chance to speak. 

239
00:20:34,480 --> 00:20:40,490
 No one... believed me. 

240
00:20:48,430 --> 00:20:50,480
 Don't die. 

241
00:20:50,480 --> 00:20:53,250
 I'll find you a heart. 

242
00:20:54,890 --> 00:21:00,050
 It was you who held my hand that day at the emergency room, wasn't it? 

243
00:21:01,130 --> 00:21:03,950
 When I fainted in the phone booth, 

